    "text": "$$\nS_2 = \\int_{0}^{40} [f(x) + 60] dx = \\int_{0}^{40} \\left[ \\frac{1}{700}x^3 - \\frac{3}{35}x^2 + \\frac{39}{28}x - 30 + 60 \\right] dx = 1400 \\text{ m}^2.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      155,
      401,
      500,
      489
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Vậy tỉ số $\\frac{S_1}{S_2} = \\frac{600}{1400} = \\frac{3}{7}$."
